name: A mixture of peroxyacetic acid, hydrogen peroxide, and 1-hydroxyethylidine-1,1-diphosphonic acid, with or without an optional adjuvant system composed of a mixture dimethyl sebacate (up to 20 percent by weight), dimethyl succinate (up to 0.8 percent by weight), dimethyl adipate (68-76 percent by weight) and dimethyl glutarate (4-12 percent by weight).
